                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-209-off1217 t18210912-209-cd1218"></join>, one bedstead, value 10 s.; the frame of a four-post bedstead, value 10 s.; one leather bag, value 3 s., and one sack, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210912-209-victim2028" type="victimName">
